Package: collatzR
Type: Package
Title: Package for implementing Collatz conjucture 
Version: 1.0.0.1
Date: 2023-09-24
Authors@R: 
    person("Sulman", "Owili", , "s.owili@cgiar.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7401-5326"))
Author: Sulman Owili [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Sulman Owili <s.owili@cgiar.org>
Description: A package for exploring and visualizing the Collatz conjecture, a fascinating mathematical sequence. It provides functions for: (1) determining if a number is whole, even, or odd, (2) performing the Collatz operation on the selected number, (3) generating Collatz sequences for various starting numbers, (4) generating the maximum value in the Collatz sequence for various starting numbers, (5) generating the total number of steps in the Collatz sequence required to reach 1 for various starting numbers,and (6) visualizing the seguence for the selected number.
